   "[Writing Styles] Likes": {"1": "Conversational tone using informal language, e.g., 'Hi there! Hope you're having a great day!'", "2": "Positive valence, focusing on opportunities, e.g., 'I’m excited to share some new offerings with you!'", "3": "Emojis for engagement, e.g., 'Looking forward to seeing you soon! 😊'", "4": "Personal anecdotes that relate to community, e.g., 'As a fellow Clark County resident...'", "5": "Clear, straightforward wording, e.g., 'Please let me know if you have any questions.'"},
